e="font-weight: bold;">Howard Bilton</span><br><br>Co-Founder &amp; Entrepeneur</span></h3><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-109_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-111_">Howard is a businessman from Yorkshire now living in Hong Kong, an enthusiastic wine lover and admirer of Portugal’s wines especially from the Alentejo region.
